The @library{one-dimension} library implements low level operations over
generalised ranges of value for a coordinate.  It can be used to operate
ranges of numbers or characters or whatever objects upon which we can
define an ordering.  @library{one-dimension} is the backbone of the
@library{char-sets} library.

